oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Rick Riman tapes - tape 2 of 5 - Side two - Channel one
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Bluegrass performances collected by Rick Riman. On loan from Craig S. Wales. Party at Dillards' house in Topanga Canyon, Caliifornia on May 7 and 8, 1963 continued from side one. Performers as listed on insert include Bill Keith (banjo), Doug Dillard (banjo), Bob Yellin (banjo), Kenny Baker (fiddle), Tracy Schwartz (fiddle) -- Dean Webb (mandolin), Del McCoury (guitar), Clarence White (guitar), Rodney Dillard (guitar), Skip Conover (dobro), Roger Bush (bass).
